articles.title: Nepal president dissolves parliament; announces mid-term polls in November - Times of India
articles.description: South Asia News: KATHMANDU: In a dramatic turn of events, Nepal President Bidya Devi Bhandari on Friday midnight dissolved the parliament and announced mid-term polls .
